block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Learn how to fold an Origami Skull Mask designed by Kunihiko Kasahara. This skull mask is also great as a Halloween decoration too. Perfect for Halloween. Less than a minute origami. As usual, Enjoy!!! Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee@Heap Art
